category: Text
requires: cygwin libfst1 libgcc1 libstdc++6
sdesc: "Tool for Bayesian non-parametric word segmentation and language model learning using Pitman-Yor language models"
ldesc: "latticelm, a tool for Bayesian non-parametric word segmentation and
language model learning using Pitman-Yor language models. The major point of
the toolkit is that it is applicable to not only regular text, but also
lattices."
